    <div class="main review-item" id="6666968">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6666968/" class="title-link">中世纪并不黑，而且现代西欧文明形成的脉络清晰可见</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6666968"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2687002/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2687002-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2687002/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">顾澜</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-05-12"
      class="main-meta">2014-05-12 18:24:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6666968_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  首先讲讲这书的几个优点： 1 体系庞大，细节精准。对于历史有特别爱好，不满足于咀嚼别人抽离提取观点之后的极简历史书的同学尤其推荐。 2 可读性较高。有些细节和专有名词翻译不够准确，但由于翻译得至少像中国人说的话，加上书本身叙述有趣，读起来像小说一般酣畅淋漓。 ps，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6666968/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">16有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6666968_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6666968_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





